{"tid":754171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(網上瘋傳) 大陸賣假疫苗身家300億 　女董兒媳炫富爽開粉紅勞斯萊斯","createTime":"2018-07-24T07:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T06:24:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":117,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"1de5e5725fc12dfdb41f8c5bc35e15619c77d477","tid":754171,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-07-24/450/20180724001646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-07-24%2F450%2F20180724001646.jpg&h=270241c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">被逮賣假疫苗累積300億身家的女董兒媳，被爆是「扒皮女」炫富」粉紅勞斯萊斯。（圖／翻攝微博） </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-07-24/590/20180724001650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-07-24%2F590%2F20180724001650.jpg&h=e8966eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-07-24/450/20180724001653.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-07-24%2F450%2F20180724001653.jpg&h=78995be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-07-24/590/20180724001656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-07-24%2F590%2F20180724001656.jpg&h=2ef9676c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國大陸長春「長生生技」公司被爆生產狂犬病假疫苗，女董高俊芳與4名高層全被拘捕，事件引發恐慌。身家67億人民幣（約新台幣302億元）的高俊芳，背景全被起底，尤其兒媳生活超奢侈，微博中全是炫富曬名牌照片，網友痛罵「再貴的香水也掩蓋不了你的人渣味」！<br />\n<br />\n有網友爆料，高俊芳兒子張洛豪養的小三隋嘉琪，是個可怕「扒皮女」，擠走元配成正宮，張洛豪除了疫苗事業，還有一個豪車隊，玩的都是超跑，在北京、香港、長春都有房，隋嘉琪長年世界遊玩，買包買車毫不手軟。<br />\n<br />\n隋女微博隨即遭肉搜曝光，上傳的照片讓人大開眼界，不僅勞斯萊斯是訂製的粉紅色，還有藍寶堅尼等超跑，連到瑞士玩，也是搭直升機上少女峰。爆料引發瘋傳，網友紛紛痛批隋女生活奢侈「再貴的香水也掩蓋不了你的人渣味」、「拿別人的命錢奢華，這是對生命褻瀆」、「這些人已無人性，用吸血鬼來形容再合適不過。」、「還不罰個傾家蕩產」、「罰300多萬是來搞笑的嗎」揚言「死刑」、「這種人應該株連九族」。<br />\n<br />\n長生生技爆發生產狂犬病、百白破（百日咳、白喉、破傷風）三合一假疫苗後，風暴延燒，讓大陸領導人親上火線發言重批，大陸國家主席習近平則說：「總理李克強也批示稱，事件突人的道德底線，必須給人民明白交代。」看來隋女昔日極盡奢侈的生活，恐成過眼雲煙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180724001640-260402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180724001640-260402&d=%2FrI7eD%2F6V29ZkNZAC5nNgHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=34b5dc5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180724001640-260402</a>"},{"pid":"a6556de0b14e5b282cb1e1530a082bba3ec6e4a0","tid":754171,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":42,"score":-40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/N9TugrBvoLSlHFANkqOXAA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDczO2g9NzA0/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/ee7d0f73725ea8e46bf78c80127c4dcd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FN9TugrBvoLSlHFANkqOXAA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDczO2g9NzA0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fee7d0f73725ea8e46bf78c80127c4dcd&h=db71885f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11c07f15da0ae40332428b0f9682f814fcf98709","tid":754171,"uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:52:10.000Z","msg":"幾緊下"},{"pid":"74316ac4021bd4c87b378f9070b86fad31c81d22","tid":754171,"uid":26773,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:52:19.000Z","msg":"做雞都唔掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44753483d646f93d02bf41969a78b0ed83b7f759","tid":754171,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3435/d3435906.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3435%2Fd3435906.jpg&h=80c2e860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3435/d3435892.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna